column5: Any body up for a fish tomorrow. Going off BP.  No walking. Have  two sled and heat. No charming personality required. Need gear and valid drivers licence and how to ride a sled.
I'm off alweek. So any more volunteers.. Was thinking of lake of bays too. not to long of a road trip.
Im off march break too. LOL
Thanks for the day Paul. Good seeing you again. Man that white fish was a bigg,n. Too bad we didn't have a bigger hole to get it out. 10" just didn't cut it. LOL
I'll weld some blades to the sides. Get a quarter inch more should do.
Well you get that done, and lets hook up again. We now know the spot.
